Private Sub Filter_Change()
    On Error Goto Filter_Change_Err
    
    On Error GoTo Filter_Change_Err
    
    FillList
    
    Exit Sub

Filter_Change_Err:
    Call RegistrarError(Err.number, Err.Description, "frmSpawnList.Filter_Change", Erl)
    Resume Next
    
    Exit Sub
Filter_Change_Err:
